1. setup
create canvas
background colour

2. hair
hair black
create ellipse above head
make sure ellipse is larger than head
rectangle with the value pos

3. face
colour skin tone
create ellipse, circle in center

4. eyes
colour white
create ellipse
situate at left side
colour white
create ellipse
situate at right side of head

5. pupils
colour black
create ellipse
same center as left eye
colour black
create ellipse
same center as right eye

6. nose
colour a shade darker than skin tone
create semicircle
place near center of face

7. eyebrows
colour black
create semicircle, upside down
above left eye 
colour black
create semicircle
above right eye

8. ears
colour skin tone
attatch to edge of face left
colour skin tone
attatch to edge of face right

9. mouth
empty semicircle
colour border brown, red, or pink
create semicircle

10. mousewheel event
pos value will add according to mouse mouseWheel